Package: reach.network
Title: River Network Diagram Tools for OS NGD Water Network Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Environment Agency", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "floodforecasting@environment-agency.gov.uk")
Description: Builds simplified schematic and spatial network diagrams from
    OS NGD Water Network data. Handles gauge snapping (with explicit exclusion
    of rain gauges), optional model metadata annotation, and produces both
    static (PNG) and interactive (HTML) outputs. Part of the flode ecosystem.
